    <rigor-reason>Significant refactor of EventsPage from ~1500 lines to ~150; framework adoption proof point; ADR-021/022/026/028</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Touches `src/solutions/EventsPage/src/App.tsx` exclusively; serial integration of framework</parallel-reason>
