  <prompt>
    Rewrite `src/solutions/EventsPage/src/App.tsx` as a ~150-line thin host that: registers Event-specific handlers (`BulkUpdateEventStatus` for Mark Complete / Cancel / Reassign / Archive that the existing `executeBulkStatusUpdate` supports), mounts the Calendar pane in `Xrm.App.sidePanes`, and passes `configId={<from task 030>}` to `<DataGrid />`. Drops `IEventRecord` interface. Calendar pane mutual exclusivity with Event detail pane preserved.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in Custom Page React 18, MDA side pane lifecycle (`Xrm.App.sidePanes`), and Spaarke framework adoption patterns.
  </role>

  <goal>
    `App.tsx` is ≤200 lines, no `IEventRecord`, Calendar pane preserved, `BulkUpdateEventStatus` handler registered, all 4 modes (system / dialog / embedded / standalone) work, record-link bug closed.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per FR-MIG-02 + FR-MIG-04. The existing `App.tsx` is ~1500 lines of Event-specific grid + filter + CRUD + Calendar logic. Most of it now lives in the framework. The new App.tsx is a thin shell: URL param parse → register handlers → mount FluentProvider + DataGrid + Calendar pane (in Xrm.App.sidePanes). Per design.md §11.5.3, the 4 CRUD operations (`openNewEventForm`, `deleteSelectedEvents`, `executeBulkStatusUpdate`, `openEventDetailPane`) move to framework defaults; only `BulkUpdateEventStatus` (the multi-status registry handler) needs Event-specific registration.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/solutions/EventsPage/src/App.tsx</file>
      <file>src/solutions/EventsPage/src/registerEventHandlers.ts</file>
      <file>src/solutions/EventsPage/src/main.tsx</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 only; tokens; dark mode.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-022">React-16-safe imports avoided in framework code; Custom Page can use React 18.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-026">Vite + vite-plugin-singlefile + React 19 pattern (existing EventsPage already on this).</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-028">All BFF calls via authenticatedFetch (if EventsPage uses BFF; otherwise XrmDataverseClient default).</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">App.tsx ≤200 lines.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">No `IEventRecord` interface in App.tsx — generic record handling only.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Calendar pane mutual exclusivity with Event detail pane preserved.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">`rowOpen` default (`webResource`) from configjson — uses `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo({pageType:"webresource"})` for record links → bug closure.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-021-fluent-design-system.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-022-pcf-platform-libraries.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-026-full-page-custom-page-standard.md</file>
      <file>.claude/adr/ADR-028-spaarke-auth-architecture.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/ui/fluent-v9-component-authoring.md</file>
